{"tid":1766184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩撞到有手足比人捉","createTime":"2019-12-02T11:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:13:39.000Z","uid":202633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce261f0db89bb365eeffea87848488886add22e","tid":1766184,"uid":202633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"我就係油麻地站同女朋友出站<br />\n行左一兩步見到個中學生咁既年紀手足 比人捉住<br />\n跟住有個藍絲女人係到講<br />\n我見到佢跳閘架<br />\n個藍絲女人再同啲黨鐵外籍foodpanda講<br />\nU can check his octopus card<br />\n跟住行左一陣 手足就甩身跑走咗<br />\n我全程係後面吊住尾 睇住手足<br />\n想上去幫手時 佢就咁岩跑走<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n係黨鐵or係街見到有手足比人搞 尤其係啲閪藍絲<br />\n就唔該快啲去圍埋係咁嘴遁 幫手<br />\n比機會手足跑走<br />\n <br />\n香港人幫香港人"},{"pid":"9768885a5ef615dd568991e7089e190d1e3108d2","tid":1766184,"uid":100205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"香港人幫香港人"},{"pid":"4aa8d26bcf0286d232921d55df3ebbb748d761a0","tid":1766184,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"大家見到呢啲情況真係要幫手<br />\n手足被狗圍 大家未必敢 但藍絲真係唔使驚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244484b4a5c821f4b85885affea493bffd5e37fb","tid":1766184,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"講緊邊隻online game?"},{"pid":"162a4956fb074ce1cb8bd6284ac3012f485eba5f","tid":1766184,"uid":202633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"真係唔好得個睇字 適當時候上去幫手"},{"pid":"7ae01d8cc6f655f90468f99bb3eafa5046a63008","tid":1766184,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9768885a5ef615dd568991e7089e190d1e3108d2","tid":1766184,"uid":100205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"香港人幫香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"香港人幫香港人"},{"pid":